 <sect2>
  <title>Bug fixes</title>
  <itemizedlist>
   <listitem>
    <!--
    2020-08-12 [0462d90]
    -->
    <para>
     At pgpool startup, if pid file exists, truncate pid file to zero length before writing. (Bo Peng)
    </para>
