    </para>
   </listitem>

   <listitem>
    <!--
    2020-08-11 [81b1e3e]
    -->
    <para>
     Fix <xref linkend="guc-connection-life-time"> does not work if primary node is not 0 in streaming replication mode. (Tatsuo Ishii)
    </para>
